features: 【 Multifunctional Storage Chest 】 The bedroom dresser can be used as a nightstand, wardrobe, entrance table, office supplies storage cabinet, bedside cabinet, and sofa table. A lightweight bedside table is the perfect home decoration for bedrooms, living rooms, and dormitories.

【 Large storage space 】 The rustic dresser has 9 storage drawers, each measuring 10.2"x10.2" x11". You can use it to store various items such as books, clothes, toys, and miscellaneous items, making your room look clean and tidy. The top can be used to place alarms, phones, decorations, and more.
【 Easy to assemble 】 The chest of drawers size is 33.7 "X 11" X 39.4 ", and the package contains detailed instructions and tools for installation. It can be installed quickly in just 30 minutes.

【 Stable Structure 】 The closet dresser is assembled from high-quality stainless steel pipes and plastic connectors, with a sturdy and durable structure. The top is covered with a fabric cover, which can withstand a weight of 25LB. The storage shelves is lightweight and easy to move to different spaces.
【 Fashion Design 】 The clothes organizer with printed patterns can easily match any home style, making it an excellent storage solution choice for any family, small apartment or university dormitory.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wasn’t that bad
reviews.reviewText: So, as I opened the packaging it looked like an IKEA puzzle. I was about to tape it up and send it back! But I thought I’d give it a go. So happy I did! I read the instructions which were not that difficult to follow actually and I am not one that buys stuff and puts it together. I will pay the extra money for someone else to do it. It took me the better part of 1 evening but I did it and I love it! You definitely need to have a mallet or hammer to tighten everything up which I did and it looks great! Just like the picture. I just now purchased the night stand that matches it. It truly wasn’t that difficult but for me it was time consuming because I do not build things, ever! I love how it looks, it works great and it is exactly as I had hoped.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fit in anywhere colorful nine drawer dresser.
reviews.reviewText: On moving in the past, I gave away my dresser as it did not fit with all the shelving I had in the new apt.Moving back to where I was a year later, needed a dresser so I decided on this as it fit perfectly in the space I had and was durable enough for the clothing I needed space for.Just love the colored fronts on the drawers and I'm able to set a few things on top.Would definitely recommend for bedroom or even child's room for space saving.

reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. It went together easily, I love the multi colors on the front and it’s perfect for just oddball storage of stuff. You could also use it for a dresser in a bedroom.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Ohhhhh no this outcome made me very , very sad
reviews.reviewText: I was sooo looking forward to having this. The dimensions were perfect, and I loved how it looked in the picture. Sadly, after 30 minutes of trying to get it together , with a hammer as they suggested, the pieces just were not going to join up together. I worked so hard on it I was sweating . I was only 4 diagrams into it and nothing I did would work. I have put together so many pieces of furniture over decades, but this one just didn't work. I packed it up, and immediately took it to the UPS store to return it. The return was very easy, and the refund was done within minutes. So, now I'm still on the hunt.
